http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Kochi/Children%E2%80%99s-park-to-get-a-facelift/article14010016.ece

Ernakulam Children’s Park, recreation pond on its premises and Marine Drive walkway will now get a facelift.A meeting of the District Tourism Promotion Council presided by its chairman District Collector M. G. Rajamanickam here on Tuesday decided to implement the project by seeking Rs. 6 crore assistance from the Tourism Department.An official issued release said that the children’s park will have facilities for go-karting, sky cycling, bumper car ride, boat riding, shooting range, archery, roller skating hockey, rope climbing, elevated gallery, and open air auditorium.Forest Industries Travancore Ltd will be the agency responsible for executing the renovation project. S. Gopakumar, noted architect, presented the project report. Hibi Eden, MLA, will lead a committee for getting the funds from the Tourism Department and ensuring the timely completion of the project.